Name: Unity Pomodoro
About the game: Unity Pomodoro is an open source countdown timer app created in Unity designed primarily for desktop use. Unity Pomodoro is a time management tool based on the pomodoro technique, the aim is to improve your productivity by introducing timers for both your work and break sessions. Quickly swap between the two timers to keep you on track and focused.
